p1 = (11,10,4), p2 = (12,7,2), p3 = (13,12,3)
\overrightarrow{p_1p_2} = \left( \begin{array}{c}12\\ 7\\ 2 \end{array} \right) - \left( \begin{array}{c}11\\ 10\\ 4\\ \end{array} \right) = \left( \begin{array}{c}1\\ -3\\ -2\\ \end{array} \right)
 \overrightarrow{p_1p_3} = \left( \begin{array}{c}13\\ 12\\ 3\\ \end{array} \right) - \left( \begin{array}{c}11\\ 10\\ 4\\ \end{array} \right) = \left( \begin{array}{c}2\\ 2\\ -1\\ \end{array} \right) 
E: \overrightarrow{x} = \overrightarrow{p_1} + r \cdot \overrightarrow{p_1p_2} + s \cdot\overrightarrow{p_1p_3}
\left( \begin{array}{c}0\\ x\\ 0\\ \end{array} \right)
\overrightarrow{x} = \left( \begin{array}{c}0\\ x\\ 0\\ \end{array} \right)
